# DuckXR â€” Whisper model requirement

This project requires an OpenAI Whisper Tiny model binary to be downloaded and placed locally before running any speech / transcription features.

Download links (official):
- Hugging Face Whisper models and data from https://huggingface.co/unity/inference-engine-whisper-tiny/tree/main/models (this is the tiny variant)
- Additional Hugging Face Whisper model data: https://huggingface.co/unity/inference-engine-whisper-tiny/tree/main/data 

Recommended placement
- Place the whisper model inside: ./AI Models/models
- Place the vocab.json inside: ./AI Models/data

Usage notes
- Whisper model needs to be assigned to the RunWhisper.cs fields accordingly
